thread.title: Stephanie
thread.title_full: Avery WePrint Australia reviewed by Stephanie

author: Stephanie
title: Stephanie
text:
It was really easy for me to create my labels online as they already had a template that met my needs. They arrived intact and within a few days of ordering.
It really was ease and grace and I was very happy with the end result.
I would like to see more templates available and a larger range of label sizes...but i'm sure it could all be sorted with a phone call to customer service.
